title: North Korea FIRES ballistic missile into the sea | Daily Mail Online
text: show ad 'The US stands behind Japan, its great ally, 100%': Trump and Japanese PM hold conference to denounce 'absolutely intolerable' North Korea missile test North Korea fired a ballistic missile into the sea off its east coast early on Sunday, South Korea's military said U.S. and South Korean military sources said the missile did not appear to be an Intercontinental Ballistic Missile (ICBM) given its flight range Trump said: 'The United States of America stands behind Japan, its great ally, 100 per cent, thank you'
